headline.print_headline: Oracle Fiscal 3Q Net Income Rises 2 Pct
headline.main: Oracle Fiscal 3Q Net Income Rises 2 Pct

lead_paragraph: Oracle said Tuesday its fiscal third-quarter net income rose 2 percent, helped by higher cloud software subscription revenue, but investors wanted more growth and the company's stock fell in late trading.
